<br />I don't really know about all the digital signing business like you're saying.  But I can say I've plugged dozens of homemade USB projects directly into my 64bit Windows 7 machine.  But they may be covered by all this with <a href="http://www.obdev.at/products/vusb/index.html" class="postlink">VUSB's certificates.</a>

		

